Subject: [PATCH 45/51] Align bridge headers with generated bindings

---
 chrome/browser/cbf/bridge/cbf_bridge.h     |  4 ----
 chrome/browser/cbf/bridge/cbf_bridge_ffi.h | 13 +++++++++++++
 2 files changed, 13 insertions(+), 4 deletions(-)

diff --git a/chrome/browser/cbf/bridge/cbf_bridge.h b/chrome/browser/cbf/bridge/cbf_bridge.h
index 2acd0447f72b7..f173223c053aa 100644
--- a/chrome/browser/cbf/bridge/cbf_bridge.h
+++ b/chrome/browser/cbf/bridge/cbf_bridge.h
